---
import Section from './Section.astro';
import { about } from '../data/content';
---
<Section id="about" title={about.title}>
  <div class="about-body">
    <p>
      Engineer at <strong>Denso, Tokyo</strong>. I build systems that hold up under pressure —
      cloud infra, full-stack apps, the whole stack. IIT Hyderabad by training,
      <strong>AWS Certified</strong> by choice, slightly too invested in clean architecture by habit.
    </p>
    <p>
      Originally from Jodhpur, India. Now living in Japan, which has been equal parts
      humbling and fascinating. Off the keyboard: football, table tennis, swimming —
      anything that requires you to think fast and adapt faster.
    </p>
    <p>
      I like systems that are boring in production. That's the goal.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-body strong {
    color: var(--accent-4);
  }

  .about-body em {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .about-body p { font-size: 0.97rem; }
  }
</style>
